Class ClientPutBase

java.lang.Object
  freenet.node.fcp.ClientRequest

ClientBaseCallback, ClientPutCallback, ClientEventListener
Direct Known Subclasses:
ClientPut, ClientPutDir
public abstract class ClientPutBase
extends ClientRequest
implements ClientPutCallback, ClientEventListener

Base class for ClientPut and ClientPutDir. Any code which can be shared between the two goes here.
